videos.headline: Minnesota scores early with deep ball
videos.description: Minnesota QB Tanner Morgan airs it out deep to Rashod Bateman who catches the ball in stride and runs in for a 51-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Minnesota scores early with deep ball) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin fumbles ball on wildcat
videos.description: With Aron Cruickshank taking the snap, he gets hit in the backfield and fumbles the ball, with Minnesota recovering.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin fumbles ball on wildcat) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor backs into end zone for TD reception
videos.description: Jack Coan throws it downfield to Jonathan Taylor, who catches the ball and backs into the end zone for a 28-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor backs into end zone for TD reception) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cephus makes TD grab in snowy conditions
videos.description: With the snow falling in Minnesota, Wisconsin's Jack Coan throws deep to Quintez Cephus, who reaches out to make the catch and score a 47-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cephus makes TD grab in snowy conditions) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Wisconsin gets tricky on TD drive
videos.description: Wisconsin runs a reverse on a kickoff return that ends up in Minnesota territory, then the Badgers use the end-around with Kendric Pryor scoring from 26 yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Wisconsin gets tricky on TD drive) 2019/11/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Taylor pads lead with 11-yard score
videos.description: Jonathan Taylor finds the crease and runs into the end zone to extend Wisconsin's lead to 31-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Taylor pads lead with 11-yard score) 2019/11/30 ESHEET
